	<p>As a new company it&#8217;s so great to have resources like this from people like you.</p>


</div>
</li>
	<li><div class="even">
	<p class="permlink"><a href="http://24ways.org/2008/contract-killer#c004439" id="c004439">12/02/2010</a></p>
	<h4><a href="http://www.mcgarvey.co.uk"><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=dcdf3acd536db648e86ef151745e0f08&amp;size=100&amp;default=http%3A%2F%2Fcloud.24ways.org%2Fimg%2Fgravatar.png" class="gravatar" alt="" height="100" width="100" /> John McGarvey - web copywriter <small>http://www.mcgarvey.co.uk</small></a></h4>
		<p>I stumbled upon this post when I was searching for sample contracts for freelancers. I&#8217;m really impressed with it &#8211; so much in fact that I&#8217;ve susbtantially adapted it so it&#8217;s suitable for copywriters (like me) and posted it up on my own site:</p>

	<p>http://www.mcgarvey.co.uk/2010/01/11/download-my-plain-english-copywriting-contract/</p>

	<p>Thanks for sharing this and offering it up for anyone to use!</p>

	<p>Cheers,</p>

	<p>John.</p>


</div>
</li>
	<li><div class="odd">
	<p class="permlink"><a href="http://24ways.org/2008/contract-killer#c004489" id="c004489">26/02/2010</a></p>
	<h4><a href=""><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=c1d2bc9c2dc4c87ce61741374a668539&amp;size=100&amp;default=http%3A%2F%2Fcloud.24ways.org%2Fimg%2Fgravatar.png" class="gravatar" alt="" height="100" width="100" /> Natasha Hanna <small></small></a></h4>
		<p>Great article! It was really helpful in explaining what should be contained in a contract and the importance of having one.</p>

	<p>Very good reading for those of us still in college.</p>

	<p>Thanks!</p>


</div>
</li>
	<li><div class="even">
	<p class="permlink"><a href="http://24ways.org/2008/contract-killer#c004626" id="c004626">27/04/2010</a></p>
	<h4><a href="http://www.ursusmedia.co.uk"><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=bfb01b3424ad940a02a1dc724e7120b0&amp;size=100&amp;default=http%3A%2F%2Fcloud.24ways.org%2Fimg%2Fgravatar.png" class="gravatar" alt="" height="100" width="100" /> Lucy Wilkinson <small>http://www.ursusmedia.co.uk</small></a></h4>
		<p>Blimey, reading that was a real blast of fresh air. Thank you for making it public. Good work fella!</p>


</div>
</li>
</ul>

